$TXTM The power of the marathon thinking... y'all know i'm proud of my purchase of some $AAPL many years ago... but the long term thinking takes so much stress out of the daily ups and downs. 
 
I've seen my portfolio go from $10k up to $200k and then drop way back down $50k some times due to price fluctuations.  
 
But knowing what you own and thinking 5-10 years down the road makes those down periods just so freaking easy. It is a mindset change for many... but oh so worth it IMHO. 
 
Hemp is a revolution. Once people see the power, mindsets change. Hope comes in and stays. 
 
I feel so much guilt over plastics for example. Every time I think about how much oil (a non-renewable resource) goes in to plastics and then goes in the dump (or in the ocean), I get real mad at what we've done to our kids.  
 
But hemp has the power to change that. 
 
And 
 
So many other things too!
